{"tid":2288501,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"外國遠足同香港遠足","createTime":"2020-11-16T13:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:45:24.000Z","uid":324681,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e24e8ab98eabe2f0ee434e0a10ba66e01277d70","tid":2288501,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"香港行山，除非爆林，多數跟著條路行。<br />\n外國果D行山係咪同香港一樣都有條路俾你行。<br />\n定係本身冇特定路線只係自己靠指南針方向嚮樹林度行?"},{"pid":"05d50e482488673e2dd3cce62c9dab9b33f3d6b9","tid":2288501,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"外國其他出名既路線 多數都會有路牌同清晰既路<br />\n<br />\n去過日本行山+露營<br />\n會有路牌指示<br />\n同埋條路有人keep住行(唔多 但係有人keep住行就會keep到條路)<br />\n條路算係幾明顯<br />\n去到某d位好僻 少人既路線會有絲帶帶路(大概每50m會有一條)<br />\n但係會唔會行錯真係憑感覺<br />\n因為去到呢d位條路唔會好明顯"},{"pid":"2f2fad371dac438b0e9fc4e05234259998940247","tid":2288501,"uid":262575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T02:53:12.000Z","msg":"多數有指示，行唔行到係另一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1557e03937ed4ae6de68f0b8b89bfa6196193d3d","tid":2288501,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f2fad371dac438b0e9fc4e05234259998940247","tid":2288501,"uid":262575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T02:53:12.000Z","msg":"多數有指示，行唔行到係另一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c093213239ca91c7c1c9f6ec538b0681c3730d8e","tid":2288501,"uid":262575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1557e03937ed4ae6de68f0b8b89bfa6196193d3d","tid":2288501,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f2fad371dac438b0e9fc4e05234259998940247","tid":2288501,"uid":262575,"like":3,"dislike":1